location.zh-cn: 今牡丹江、绥芬河及长白山一带

description.zh-cn: 明代女真族三大部之一，主要由胡里改部和斡朵里部等构成。后在努尔哈赤的领导下统一，并成为后金及清朝的核心力量。
description.en: One of the three major Jurchen tribes during the Ming Dynasty, primarily composed of the Huligai and Odoli tribes. They were later unified under the leadership of Nurhaci and became the core force of the Later Jin and the Qing Dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 中国历史上的一个朝代。在东北地区设立羁縻卫所，对女真各部进行管辖。
description.en: A dynasty in Chinese history. It established Jimi Guards and Posts in the Northeast region to govern the Jurchen tribes.

description.zh-cn: 中国东北地区的古代民族，明代时期分为建州、海西、野人三部。
description.en: An ancient people in Northeast China, divided into three main groups during the Ming Dynasty: Jianzhou, Haixi, and Yeren.

description.zh-cn: 明代女真族三大部之一。
description.en: One of the three major Jurchen tribes during the Ming Dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 明代女真族三大部之一。
description.en: One of the three major Jurchen tribes during the Ming Dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 建州女真的一部，曾是建州女真最后一个被努尔哈赤消灭的强大对手。
description.en: A tribe of the Jianzhou Jurchens, it was the last powerful opponent within the Jianzhou Jurchens to be eliminated by Nurhaci.

description.zh-cn: 辽金时代的部落，为完颜部附庸，建州女真的主要组成部分。
description.en: A tribal confederation during the Liao and Jin dynasties, a vassal of the Wanyan tribe, and a major component of the Jianzhou Jurchens.

description.zh-cn: 建州女真的重要部落，元代为胡里改万户府，明初南迁归附明朝。
description.en: An important tribe of the Jianzhou Jurchens, known as the Huligai Wanhu Fu in the Yuan Dynasty. It migrated south and submitted to the Ming Dynasty in the early Ming period.

description.zh-cn: 建州女真的重要部落，猛哥帖木儿为其首领，元代为斡朵里万户府，明初南迁归附明朝。
description.en: An important tribe of the Jianzhou Jurchens, led by Möngke Temür. It was known as the Odoli Wanhu Fu during the Yuan Dynasty and migrated south to submit to the Ming Dynasty in the early Ming period.

description.zh-cn: 中国历史上由蒙古族建立的王朝。曾在女真地区设立万户府进行管辖。
description.en: A dynasty in Chinese history established by the Mongols. It set up Wanhu Fu (myriarchies) to govern the Jurchen areas.

description.zh-cn: 元朝设立的行中书省，管辖包括女真地区在内的中国东北部。
description.en: A province (branch secretariat) established by the Yuan Dynasty, which administered northeastern China, including the Jurchen territories.

description.zh-cn: 元代于五国部旧地设立的女真万户府之一。
description.en: One of the Jurchen myriarchies (Wanhu Fu) established by the Yuan Dynasty in the former territory of the Wuguobu.

description.zh-cn: 元代于五国部旧地设立的女真万户府之一。
description.en: One of the Jurchen myriarchies (Wanhu Fu) established by the Yuan Dynasty in the former territory of the Wuguobu.

description.zh-cn: 元代于五国部旧地设立的女真万户府之一。
description.en: One of the Jurchen myriarchies (Wanhu Fu) established by the Yuan Dynasty in the former territory of the Wuguobu.

description.zh-cn: 胡里改部酋长，明初率部归附明朝。
description.en: Chieftain of the Huligai tribe who led his people to submit to the Ming Dynasty in the early Ming period.

description.zh-cn: 斡朵里部酋长，爱新觉罗氏先祖，明初率部归附明朝。
description.en: Chieftain of the Odoli tribe, an ancestor of the Aisin Gioro clan, who led his people to submit to the Ming Dynasty in the early Ming period.

description.zh-cn: 明朝设立的羁縻卫所，建州三卫之一，以胡里改部为中心建立。
description.en: A Jimi Guard established by the Ming Dynasty, one of the Three Guards of Jianzhou, established with the Huligai tribe as its center.

description.zh-cn: 明朝设立的羁縻卫所，建州三卫之一，由斡朵里部分置而成。
description.en: A Jimi Guard established by the Ming Dynasty, one of the Three Guards of Jianzhou, formed from a division of the Odoli tribe.

description.zh-cn: 明朝设立的羁縻卫所，建州三卫之一，由斡朵里部分置而成。
description.en: A Jimi Guard established by the Ming Dynasty, one of the Three Guards of Jianzhou, formed from a division of the Odoli tribe.

description.zh-cn: 明朝在建州女真地区设立的建州卫、建州左卫、建州右卫三个羁縻卫所的合称。
description.en: A collective name for the three Jimi Guards established by the Ming Dynasty in the Jianzhou Jurchen region: Jianzhou Guard, Jianzhou Left Guard, and Jianzhou Right Guard.

description.zh-cn: 清朝的奠基者，统一了建州女真各部，并建立了后金政权。
description.en: The founder of the Qing Dynasty, who unified the various tribes of the Jianzhou Jurchens and established the Later Jin regime.

description.zh-cn: 由努尔哈赤发动的一系列旨在统一建州女真各部的战争。
description.en: A series of wars launched by Nurhaci aimed at unifying the various tribes of the Jianzhou Jurchens.

description.zh-cn: 建州女真八部之一。
description.en: One of the eight tribes of the Jianzhou Jurchens.

description.zh-cn: 建州女真八部之一。
description.en: One of the eight tribes of the Jianzhou Jurchens.

description.zh-cn: 女真姓氏，猛哥帖木儿所属的氏族。
description.en: A Jurchen clan to which Möngke Temür belonged.

description.zh-cn: 清朝皇室的姓氏。
description.en: The family name of the imperial house of the Qing Dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 建州女真是明代女真族三大部之一。
description.en: The Jianzhou Jurchens were one of the three major divisions of the Jurchen people during the Ming Dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 海西女真是明代女真族三大部之一。
description.en: The Haixi Jurchens were one of the three major divisions of the Jurchen people during the Ming Dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 野人女真是明代女真族三大部之一。
description.en: The Yeren Jurchens were one of the three major divisions of the Jurchen people during the Ming Dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 在辽金时代，五国部是完颜部的附庸。
description.en: During the Liao and Jin dynasties, the Wuguobu was a vassal of the Wanyan tribe.

description.zh-cn: 元朝于五国部旧地设立拖温女真万户府。
description.en: The Yuan Dynasty established the Tuowen Jurchen Myriarchy in the former territory of the Wuguobu.

description.zh-cn: 元朝于五国部旧地设立斡朵里女真万户府。
description.en: The Yuan Dynasty established the Odoli Jurchen Myriarchy in the former territory of the Wuguobu.

description.zh-cn: 元朝于五国部旧地设立胡里改女真万户府。
description.en: The Yuan Dynasty established the Huligai Jurchen Myriarchy in the former territory of the Wuguobu.

description.zh-cn: 元朝于五国部旧地设立孛苦江女真万户府。
description.en: The Yuan Dynasty established the Bokujiang Jurchen Myriarchy in the former territory of the Wuguobu.

description.zh-cn: 元朝于五国部旧地设立脱斡怜女真万户府。
description.en: The Yuan Dynasty established the Tuowolian Jurchen Myriarchy in the former territory of the Wuguobu.

description.zh-cn: 元代的拖温万户府隶属辽阳行省管辖。
description.en: The Tuowen Myriarchy of the Yuan Dynasty was under the jurisdiction of the Liaoyang province.

description.zh-cn: 元代的斡朵里万户府隶属辽阳行省管辖。
description.en: The Odoli Myriarchy of the Yuan Dynasty was under the jurisdiction of the Liaoyang province.

description.zh-cn: 元代的胡里改万户府隶属辽阳行省管辖。
description.en: The Huligai Myriarchy of the Yuan Dynasty was under the jurisdiction of the Liaoyang province.

description.zh-cn: 元代的孛苦江万户府隶属辽阳行省管辖。
description.en: The Bokujiang Myriarchy of the Yuan Dynasty was under the jurisdiction of the Liaoyang province.

description.zh-cn: 元代的脱斡怜万户府隶属辽阳行省管辖。
description.en: The Tuowolian Myriarchy of the Yuan Dynasty was under the jurisdiction of the Liaoyang province.

description.zh-cn: 元末明初，胡里改部在酋长阿哈出带领下向东南迁移归附明朝。
description.en: In the late Yuan and early Ming period, the Huligai tribe, led by chieftain Ahacu, migrated southeast and submitted to the Ming Dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 元末明初，斡朵里部在酋长猛哥帖木儿带领下向东南迁移归附明朝。
description.en: In the late Yuan and early Ming period, the Odoli tribe, led by chieftain Möngke Temür, migrated southeast and submitted to the Ming Dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 明朝以胡里改部为中心建立了建州卫。
description.en: The Ming Dynasty established the Jianzhou Guard with the Huligai tribe as its center.

description.zh-cn: 明朝将斡朵里部分置为建州左卫。
description.en: The Ming Dynasty established the Jianzhou Left Guard by partitioning the Odoli tribe.

description.zh-cn: 明朝将斡朵里部分置为建州右卫。
description.en: The Ming Dynasty established the Jianzhou Right Guard by partitioning the Odoli tribe.

description.zh-cn: 1588年，努尔哈赤攻克完颜城，消灭了其在建州女真的最后一个强大对手完颜部。
description.en: In 1588, Nurhaci conquered Wanyan city, eliminating his last powerful opponent among the Jianzhou Jurchens, the Wanyan tribe.

description.zh-cn: 阿哈出为完颜氏。
description.en: Ahacu was of the Wanyan clan.

description.zh-cn: 猛哥帖木儿为交鲁氏（觉罗氏）。
description.en: Möngke Temür was of the Gioro clan.

description.zh-cn: 猛哥帖木儿是爱新觉罗氏的先祖。
description.en: Möngke Temür is an ancestor of the Aisin Gioro clan.
